### {155}{}{I told you about the situation on that farm. Find out what's the problem and you can earn $500, interested?}
{155}{}{我告诉过你农场的情况。找出问题所在，你就能赚500美元，感兴趣吗？ -- I told you about the situation on that farm. Find out what's the problem and you can earn $500, interested?}
### {156}{}{All right, let's go.}
